{"tid":933100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果違例泊車就要留案底，可唔可以解決違泊問題？","createTime":"2018-12-08T09:37:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T11:50:20.000Z","uid":64694,"like":12,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8586bb71ba2821b08999c927ac80845be38630b7","tid":933100,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T09:37:45.000Z","msg":"我喺度諗而家點解會有咁多違泊呢？會唔會係因為啲人覺得罪款食牛肉乾嘅阻嚇性唔夠呢？噉如果違例泊車就要留案底，增加阻嚇性，會唔會就可以解決違泊問題呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94088750f93cef8af75445df08528f02c76fa0d5","tid":933100,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T09:39:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我喺度諗而家點解會有咁多違泊呢？會唔會係因為啲人覺得母<span style=\"color: red;\">罰</span>款食牛肉乾嘅阻嚇性唔夠呢？噉如果違例泊車就要留案底，增加阻嚇性，會唔會就可以解決違泊問題呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ed77186f351cfce03584259391ed6f8dc2008e6c","tid":933100,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T09:40:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我喺度諗而家點解會有咁多違泊呢？會唔會係因為啲人覺得<span style=\"color: red;\">罰</span>款食牛肉乾嘅阻嚇性唔夠呢？噉如果違例泊車就要留案底，增加阻嚇性，會唔會就可以解決違泊問題呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"aed634e762454d77a0bcd1e06c38b05e3a80872c","tid":933100,"uid":37869,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T09:41:09.000Z","msg":"留呢個案底的後果係咩先？<br />\n如果案底的影響同而家一樣<br />\n咁一定得"},{"pid":"61746112ad478a1aa2398aa59c48f65db5fb6378","tid":933100,"uid":79481,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T09:47:46.000Z","msg":"你要去到咁極端實得架<br />\n<br />\n做到咁不如<br />\n<br />\n違泊終身監禁<br />\n<br />\n亂抛垃圾終身監禁<br />\n<br />\n係室內食煙捉到終身監禁<br />\n<br />\n咁實無人做喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e08802a625b0e224657f34926c7718a9696de2a","tid":933100,"uid":37505,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T09:49:58.000Z","msg":"當個個都有案