fd0fa0e","tid":933100,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T10:13:12.000Z","msg":"真係唔怪得有啲街童會出去𠝹車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"073d7579ec99cf974955d2cd9b8d07b83aaac26b","tid":933100,"uid":139228,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T10:25:37.000Z","msg":"1. 提高罰款額，如$320&gt;$400<br />\n2. 設記名舉報(每月有限額，如5宗)<br />\n3. 舉報需以錄影形式紀錄時間日期地點車牌<br />\n4. 成功罰款既舉報人可獲獎金，如$20-$40<br />\n5. 車主/司機否認就進入司法程序，舉報人有可能需上庭作供"},{"pid":"325e5a1e2609b2c01b86e605a07307440b4675a9","tid":933100,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T10:33:41.000Z","msg":"唔排除係有貪方便而違泊既人<br />\n但除此之外因爲無停車場 焗住違泊既人都唔少囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7231b0f338d19495acbdc870f62d58e8679e188","tid":933100,"uid":223256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T10:35:41.000Z","msg":"直接坐監或笞刑<br />\n包有效"},{"pid":"764fa25e3bea891b9ba11dda3acae54e9448f2e5","tid":933100,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T10:44:10.000Z","msg":"政府長期飯票，點會要告你又要留你案底咁浪費人力物力"},{"pid":"46b6276689a61352453f783c8f833ac7575c6067","tid":933100,"uid":81424,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T10:49:18.000Z","msg":"違例泊車幾何級數咁罰<br />\n第一次$300<br />\n第二次$600<br />\n第三次$1200<br />\n如此類推<br />\n一個月冇事先可以降一級罰款<br />\n咁就冇人夠膽亂泊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060debde129183a103f92b735eed4db536a60005","tid":933100,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61746112ad478a1aa2398aa59c48f65db5fb6378","tid":933100,"uid":79481,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T09:47:46.000Z","msg":"你要去到咁極端實得架<br />\n<br />\n做到咁不如<br />\n<br />\n違泊終身監禁<br />\n<br />\n亂抛垃圾終身監禁<br />\n<br />\n係室內